      "description": "Add support for calculating the date. Examples:\r\n\r\n```\r\n{{yesterday}}\r\n{{tomorrow}}\r\n{{date-1d:YYYY-MM-DD}} // yesterday\r\n{{date+2d:YYYY-MM-DD}} // in two days\r\n{{date+1M:YYYY-MM-DD}} // next month\r\n{{date+10y:YYYY-MM-DD}} // in 10 years\r\n{{date +7d}} // use default format\r\n```\r\n\r\nSupported units:\r\n|Unit|Shorthand|\r\n|--|--|\r\nyears | y\r\nquarters | Q\r\nmonths | M\r\nweeks | w\r\ndays | d\r\nhours | h\r\nminutes | m\r\nseconds | s\r\n",
